    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give small hospitality businesses 10% VAT relief",
        "additional_details": "We feel it\u2019s unfair that small hospitality businesses can face huge VAT bills when they have a smaller turnover. We feel that bills like this can be crippling and in turn can cause closures nationally on a regular basis.",
        "background": "We feel that small hospitality businesses who turn over less than \u00a3200,000 a year face high costs when they meet the VAT threshold, particularly with the increases to national minimum wage and national insurance contribution.",
